import React from 'react'
import { Form, Container, Button} from 'react-bootstrap'


const ContactForm = () => {

    return (

        <Container>
            <Form>
                <Form.Group>
                    <Form.Control type='start_date' placeholder='Arrive' />
                </Form.Group>
                <Form.Group>
                    <Form.Control type='end_date' placeholder='Leave' />
                </Form.Group>
                <Button variant="primary" type="submit">
                    Reserve
                </Button>
            </Form>
        </Container>

    )
}

export default ContactForm
